üé® Step 1 ‚Äî Data Model for the Bubble Chart
For each topic, we compute:

x ‚Üí topic index (just spacing on the axis)

y ‚Üí average importance

r ‚Üí bubble radius (based on frequency)

label ‚Üí topic name

Example:

js
{
